{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I think they were mostly took it from well-off Jewish families because which were whoever [INAUDIBLE] to say the most obvious victims of that particular policy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was-- but there was no ghetto at this time, and the-- we still lived in our place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And generally, there was-- but I think that everything was living full of rumors and uncertainty as far as the future was concerned.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody knew anything for certain, but I think there were already rumors that a ghetto was going to be opened because I think things like that already happened in probably in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In, in Lodz, it might have happened even earlier than in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we-- I, I don't remember terribly clearly things from this early period in 1940.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The one thing that I remember is that we weren't let-- on Pesach, on Passover of 1940, I-- we went to the house of my grandparents and--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maternal grandparents, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no paternal grandparents because they both--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--died before the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even maternal-- pater-- maternal grandparent, there was only grandfather because the grandmother remained in Bialystok and with one of my mother's sister, with Aunt Dora.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they both finished later in, in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so she was not there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The grandmother was not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The grandfather-- the grandfather was on his own, but they still probably some other aunts prepared Passover meal, which they made a traditional Passover meal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which I remember that there was still the traditional Passover dishes with hard boiled eggs in salt, and-- which I actually thought was, was very nice.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the tradition of all the celebration of that, that is still a strong memory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And otherwise, I think there were, as I said, rumors of the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
